        - anything from TODO
        - or anything else...
        
        Permission
        ----------
        
        CRUD - create, read, update, delete
        
        - Admin can CRUD ALL
        - Moderator can CRUD all pages and images
        - Editor can CRUD all pages
        - Authon can CRUD only own pages
        
